  ;; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  ;; DESIGN NOTES
  ;; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

  (text "POWER:\nVIN (7-24V) via J8 barrel or J9 screw terminal -> TPS54331 buck -> +5V/3A rail.\nAMS1117-3.3 (U4) -> +3V3 rail. HUB75 powered from separate J6/J7 5V input.\nD1=5V indicator, D3=3V3 indicator."
    (at 20 305 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))))
  (text "SPI BUS:\nShared MOSI/MISO/SCK. Four independent CS lines:\nCS_S3_MCU (JMISC->S3), CS_S3_MPU (JMISC->S3), CS_C6_MCU (JMISC->C6), CS_C6_MPU (JMISC->C6).\nSoftware must ensure one master + one target active at a time."
    (at 20 317 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))))
  (text "ESP32-S3 <-> ESP32-C6 DIRECT LINK:\nUART: S3 GPIO43(TX) -> C6 GPIO4(RX), C6 GPIO5(TX) -> S3 GPIO44(RX).\nIndependent of UNO Q. C6 can push data to S3 display. S3 can trigger C6 wireless events."
    (at 20 329 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))))
  (text "I2S AUDIO (ES8388 24-bit):\nS3 GPIO5=BCLK, GPIO6=LRCLK, GPIO7=DOUT(DAC), GPIO15=DIN(ADC).\nS3 GPIO8=I2C_SDA, GPIO9=I2C_SCL (codec control). 1k pullups R5/R6.\nLOUT1/ROUT1 -> J11 line out header. LINPUT1/RINPUT1 <- J12 PDM mic header."
    (at 20 341 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))))
  (text "RPi 5 COMPATIBILITY:\nDSI/CSI0/CSI1: 22-pin 0.5mm FPC (Molex 0545821522). RPi 5 camera/display compatible.\n40-pin header (J4): STM32U585 signals 3.3V direct. QRB2210 MPU GPIO via TXS0108E (1.8V->3.3V).\nHAT ID EEPROM (U10 24C32) on pins 27(ID_SD)/28(ID_SC). 4k7 pullups R7/R8.\nNO PCIe: QRB2210 has no PCIe root complex. NVMe/PCIe HATs will not function."
    (at 20 353 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))))
  (text "ESP32-C6 RADIO:\nThread 802.15.4, Matter, Zigbee, WiFi 6 (802.11ax), BLE 5.0.\nHome Assistant compatible. IoT mesh networking.\nJ13 USB-C for flashing via USB-Serial/JTAG."
    (at 20 371 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))))
  (text "HUB75:\nU2 (74HCT245): R1,G1,B1,R2,G2,B2,CLK,LAT. U3: ADDR_A-E, OE.\nDIR=GND (A->B), ~OE=GND (always enabled). 3.3V->5V level shift."
    (at 20 383 0) (effects (font (size 1.5 1.5))))

